    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Actually Anchoring means:-\r\nThe block hashes of a private chain are periodically written into a public chain. For this purpose, not all block hashes have to be transmitted; for example, a daily match is sufficient. In the case of a manipulation within the private chain, it is possible to know which blocks can be trusted and when a manipulation has occurred. The only transmitted information is the block number and the associated block hash.\r\n",
